<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:v="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml" xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="x-apple-disable-message-reformatting">
    <title>Registration Successful</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f7fc; color: #000; padding: 20px; min-height: 100vh;">
    <div style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 8px; padding: 30px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <h2 style="color: #333; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">Registration Successful!</h2>
        
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Hello <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Congratulations! Your account has been successfully created.</p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">Here are your account details:</p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;"><strong>Email:</strong> <%=email %></p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555;">You can now log in and access all of our services.</p>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; color: #555; margin-top: 20px;">
            <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" style="background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 20px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer;">
                Log In Now
            </a>
        </p>
        
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #777; margin-top: 30px;">
            If you did not create this account, please contact support immediately.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
